headline: Industrial Packaging Stocks Q1 Results: Benchmarking Avery Dennison (NYSE:AVY)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at industrial packaging stocks, starting with Avery Dennison (NYSE:AVY).
